name: Martin Luther King
description:
The NFT market is changing rapidly and we try to make something unique for you every day, so we created these amazing art to convey one thought: we are all so different, but still the same. It is enough to look at our nft and you will not be able to tear yourself away. This collection is for those who understand themselves and are ready to discover something new, each art is unique in its own way and it will be a great addition to your collection.

ALL 1/1 NO Multiple Editions.
